should provide context:

00:11:04.706 --> 00:11:08.251
"I want to personally tell
her about my feelings."

00:11:08.293 --> 00:11:09.335
Quote.

00:11:12.714 --> 00:11:14.132
[ROROA]
Not very fair.

00:11:14.174 --> 00:11:16.718
