[LISCIA]
Ow!

00:11:22.098 --> 00:11:24.684
C'mon ladies,
that really smarts!

00:11:24.726 --> 00:11:27.520
Not you, too, Juna!

00:11:27.562 --> 00:11:28.938
The truth is...

00:11:28.980 --> 00:11:31.191
...I'm jealous of
the rest of you.

00:11:31.232 --> 00:11:32.442
How come?

00:11:32.483 --> 00:11:34.861
