protect me, as well.

00:11:40.950 --> 00:11:43.244
I guess that's just
the way things go.

00:11:43.286 --> 00:11:45.121
From now on,
whenever we have a lesson,

00:11:45.163 --> 00:11:47.957
why don't we gather
together around the table!

00:11:47.999 --> 00:11:50.710
Oh, Ai, nice job herding us.

00:11:50.752 --> 00:11:51.669
Of course!

00:11:54.088 --> 00:11:55.131
All right.

00:11:55.173 --> 00:11:58.051
Moving on, it's time
for specific instruction,

00:11:58.092 --> 00:12:00.011
and to discuss the
different ways for you all

00:12:00.053 --> 00:12:01.888
to maintain marital bliss.

00:12:01.930 --> 00:12:03.681
