my lecture all the way

00:12:48.309 --> 00:12:50.979
to the end, then as
proof of completion

00:12:51.020 --> 00:12:53.064
I will give you
each one of these.

00:12:54.816 --> 00:12:57.277
[LISCIA] Some kind of
classified documents?

00:12:57.318 --> 00:12:59.779
[JUNA] Does that say
"burn after reading"?

00:12:59.821 --> 00:13:02.323
[AISHA] Whatever's inside
sounds pretty dangerous.

00:13:02.365 --> 00:13:03.908
