In other words,
top national security secrets.

00:13:21.426 --> 00:13:23.428
Oh.

00:13:23.469 --> 00:13:24.929
Wait, what do you mean by that?

00:13:24.971 --> 00:13:27.098
[EXCEL] While usually kept
locked within his heart,

00:13:27.140 --> 00:13:29.559
his Majesty Souma's
desires for each of you

00:13:29.600 --> 00:13:31.728
are laid bare
within these pages--

00:13:31.769 --> 00:13:34.564
